name: Flipping Reality [Jam Game]
description:
Description

One has a strangely organic environment, the other has weird man-made structures, but what is real and is anything not? What are you and where are you going? Dying is scary, but what about when it's the only option?

Made in three days between the 24th and 26th for the Brackeys GameJam (2022)

Finished on the 26th of February at 6:40 PM
